<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>heated-debate — Multi-Agent Debate Engine</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');

    *,
    *::before,
    *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a0f;
      --surface: #13131e;
      --border: #1e1e30;
      --accent1: #e8611a;
      /* orange-red flame */
      --accent2: #a855f7;
      /* violet */
      --accent3: #38bdf8;
      /* sky blue */
      --text: #e8e8f0;
      --muted: #6b6b8a;
      --code-bg: #0f0f1a;
    }

    html,
    body {
      height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    /* ── Deck ── */
    .deck {
      position: relative;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .slide {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 60px 80px;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.45s ease, transform 0.45s ease;
      transform: translateY(18px);
    }

    .slide.active {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: all;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .slide.exit {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-18px);
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    /* ── Typography ── */
    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent1);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(44px, 6.5vw, 84px);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 21px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    p,
    li {
      font-size: clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 20px);
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #b0b0cc;
    }

    strong {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    code {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85em;
      background: var(--code-bg);
      padding: 2px 7px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      color: var(--accent3);
    }

    /* ── Layout helpers ── */
    .center {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cols2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1000px;
    }

    .cols3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1080px;
    }

    .stack {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mt16 {
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .mt28 {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .mt40 {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    /* ── Cards ── */
    .card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px 30px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent2);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .card-icon {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    /* ── Agent boxes ── */
    .agent-box {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 24px 26px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .agent-box::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 3px;
    }

    .agent-a::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent1), #f59e0b);
    }

    .agent-b::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent2), var(--accent3));
    }

    .agent-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .agent-a .agent-label {
      color: var(--accent1);
    }

    .agent-b .agent-label {
      color: var(--accent2);
    }

    /* ── Dial component ── */
    .dial-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .dial-step {
      flex: 1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px 12px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--surface);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .dial-step .dlabel {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .dial-step .dnum {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .dial-step .ddesc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 5px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .d5 {
      border-color: #e8611a55;
    }

    .d5 .dnum,
    .d5 .dlabel {
      color: var(--accent1);
    }

    .d4 {
      border-color: #f59e0b55;
    }

    .d4 .dnum,
    .d4 .dlabel {
      color: #f59e0b;
    }

    .d3 {
      border-color: #10b98155;
    }

    .d3 .dnum,
    .d3 .dlabel {
      color: #10b981;
    }

    .d2 {
      border-color: #38bdf855;
    }

    .d2 .dnum,
    .d2 .dlabel {
      color: var(--accent3);
    }

    .d1 {
      border-color: #a855f755;
    }

    .d1 .dnum,
    .d1 .dlabel {
      color: var(--accent2);
    }

    /* ── Code block ── */
    .codeblock {
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 22px 26px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #9090c0;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .codeblock .comment {
      color: #444466;
    }

    .codeblock .cmd {
      color: var(--accent3);
    }

    .codeblock .kw {
      color: var(--accent1);
    }

    .codeblock .str {
      color: #a3e635;
    }

    /* ── Flow diagram ── */
    .flow {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 960px;
      flex-wrap: nowrap;
    }

    .flow-node {
      flex: 1;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px 10px;
      text-align: center;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .flow-node .fn-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .flow-node .fn-title {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .flow-arrow {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 20px;
      padding: 0 6px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* ── Stat chips ── */
    .chips {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .chip {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .chip-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    /* ── Roadmap ── */
    .roadmap-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .roadmap-num {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent1), var(--accent2));
      color: white;
    }

    .roadmap-item p {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    /* ── Title slide deco ── */
    .flame-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 50% 100%, rgba(232, 97, 26, 0.18) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 20% 80%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.10) 0%, transparent 60%);
    }

    .title-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(232, 97, 26, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(232, 97, 26, 0.3);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 7px 18px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent1);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .headline-mono {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--accent1);
    }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    .nav {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 36px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(19, 19, 30, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 40px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .nav-btn {
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--muted);
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .nav-btn:hover {
      background: var(--border);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .nav-dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--border);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-dot.active {
      background: var(--accent1);
      width: 20px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    .slide-num {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      min-width: 40px;
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* ── Animated gradient text ── */
    .grad {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent1) 0%, #f59e0b 40%, var(--accent2) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    /* ── Separator line ── */
    .sep {
      width: 48px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent1), var(--accent2));
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    /* ── List ── */
    ul.nice {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    ul.nice li::before {
      content: '→';
      color: var(--accent1);
      margin-right: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="deck" id="deck">

    <!-- ── 0 · Title ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="slide active center" id="slide-0">
      <div class="flame-bg"></div>
      <div class="title-badge">🔥 Multi-Agent Debate Engine</div>
      <h1><span class="headline-mono">heated</span><span class="grad">-debate</span></h1>
      <div class="sep" style="margin: 24px auto;"></div>
      <p style="max-width:540px; font-size:clamp(17px,2vw,23px); color:#8888aa;">
        Two LLM agents argue until a great design emerges. An architect proposes. A reviewer challenges.
        A creativity dial cools round by round.
      </p>
      <div class="chips mt40">
        <div class="chip">
          <div class="chip-dot" style="background:var(--accent3)"></div>bun / TypeScript
        </div>
        <div class="chip">
          <div class="chip-dot" style="background:#f59e0b"></div>Claude · Codex
        </div>
        <div class="chip">
          <div class="chip-dot" style="background:var(--accent2)"></div>No API key needed
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 1 · The Idea ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="slide" id="slide-1">
      <div class="eyebrow">The Idea</div>
      <h2 style="max-width:700px;">Good design emerges from structured disagreement</h2>
      <div class="sep mt28"></div>
      <div class="cols2 mt28" style="max-width:860px;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏗️</div>
          <h3>Agent A — Architect</h3>
          <p>Proposes implementation plans. Refines based on feedback. Sends diffs, not full repeats.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🔍</div>
          <h3>Agent B — Reviewer</h3>
          <p>Challenges proposals, finds flaws, identifies edge cases. Forces the plan to earn its shape.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt28" style="max-width:680px; text-align:center; color:var(--muted);">
        Both agents run in the same model or across models. No shared context — each sees only what the other sends.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 2 · Round Loop ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="slide" id="slide-2">
      <div class="eyebrow">How a Debate Runs</div>
      <h2 style="max-width:640px; text-align:center;">One topic · N rounds · two voices</h2>
      <div class="mt40 flow">
        <div class="flow-node" style="border-color:#e8611a55;">
          <div class="fn-label" style="color:var(--accent1);">Input</div>
          <div class="fn-title">topic.md</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="flow-node" style="border-color:#f59e0b55;">
          <div class="fn-label" style="color:#f59e0b;">Round 1–N</div>
          <div class="fn-title">Agent A<br><span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)">proposes</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="flow-node" style="border-color:#a855f755;">
          <div class="fn-label" style="color:var(--accent2);">Round 1–N</div>
          <div class="fn-title">Agent B<br><span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)">reviews</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="flow-node" style="border-color:#38bdf855;">
          <div class="fn-label" style="color:var(--accent3);">Output</div>
          <div class="fn-title">Transcript<br><span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)">.md log</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mt40" style="max-width:840px; border-color:var(--border);">
        <p>B's response always becomes A's next prompt. No moderator — just the ping-pong of proposal and critique, with
          context carried forward via <code>--resume</code>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cols2 mt28" style="max-width:840px;">
        <div class="agent-box agent-a">
          <div class="agent-label">Agent A · Round 2</div>
          <p style="font-size:15px;">"Addressing the Decimal-from-float issue: switching constructor to
            <code>Decimal(str(price))</code> to prevent float precision drift…"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-box agent-b">
          <div class="agent-label">Agent B · Round 2</div>
          <p style="font-size:15px;">"The <code>allow_short</code> semantics are still underspecified. Does it block the
            trade or clamp position to zero? Edge case: short then long same tick."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 3 · Creativity Dial ───────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="slide center" id="slide-3">
      <div class="eyebrow">Creativity Dial</div>
      <h2>Temperature by prompt, not by API</h2>
      <p class="mt16" style="max-width:560px; color:var(--muted);">Each round injects a behavioral prefix. The dial
        cools linearly from <strong>Wild → Precise</strong> across rounds.</p>
      <div class="dial-row mt40">
        <div class="dial-step d5">
          <div class="dlabel">Wild</div>
          <div class="dnum">5</div>
          <div class="ddesc">Radical alternatives.<br>Question the premise.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dial-step d4">
          <div class="dlabel">Creative</div>
          <div class="dnum">4</div>
          <div class="ddesc">New ideas.<br>Challenge assumptions.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dial-step d3">
          <div class="dlabel">Balanced</div>
          <div class="dnum">3</div>
          <div class="ddesc">Mix ideas<br>with refinement.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dial-step d2">
          <div class="dlabel">Focused</div>
          <div class="dnum">2</div>
          <div class="ddesc">Fix issues.<br>No new directions.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dial-step d1">
          <div class="dlabel">Precise</div>
          <div class="dnum">1</div>
          <div class="ddesc">Converge.<br>Final decisions only.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mt40" style="max-width:760px; text-align:left;">
        <p>The subscription CLIs don't expose temperature. The dial is the only behavioral modulator — and it's the
          trainable signal for RL later.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 4 · Architecture ──────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="slide" id="slide-4">
      <div class="eyebrow">Architecture</div>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;">shelley.ts — the Bun engine</h2>
      <div class="cols2 mt40" style="max-width:960px; gap:30px; align-items:start;">
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="card" style="border-color:#38bdf855;">
            <h3 style="color:var(--accent3);">🦩 Claude backend</h3>
            <p>Session continuity via <code>--resume &lt;session-id&gt;</code>. New sessions with
              <code>--session-id</code> + <code>--system-prompt</code>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="border-color:#a855f755;">
            <h3 style="color:var(--accent2);">⚡ Codex backend</h3>
            <p>Stateless calls via <code>codex exec --sandbox read-only</code>. Conversation history windowed manually
              per-agent.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="border-color:#f59e0b55;">
            <h3 style="color:#f59e0b;">🔐 Env sanitation</h3>
            <p>Strips provider API keys before spawning CLIs. You stay on subscription auth — no accidental billing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="codeblock">
            <span class="comment"># Run 5 rounds, default topic</span>
            <span class="cmd">bun shelley.ts</span> <span class="str">5</span>

            <span class="comment"># Topic from file, 3 rounds</span>
            <span class="cmd">bun shelley.ts</span> <span class="kw">-f</span> debates/stock-trades/topic.md <span
              class="str">3</span>

            <span class="comment"># Switch both agents to Codex</span>
            <span class="kw">MODEL_A</span>=codex:gpt-5 <span class="kw">MODEL_B</span>=codex:gpt-5 \
            <span class="cmd">bun shelley.ts</span> <span class="kw">-f</span> debates/my-topic/topic.md <span
              class="str">5</span>

            <span class="comment"># Resume a partial run</span>
            <span class="kw">RESUME_FROM_LOG</span>=debates/my-topic/20260227_1930.md \
            <span class="cmd">bun shelley.ts</span> <span class="kw">-f</span> debates/my-topic/topic.md <span
              class="str">7</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="font-size:15px;">
            <strong>Context injection</strong><br>
            <p class="mt16">Put a <code>context.txt</code> next to your <code>topic.md</code> listing repo-relative file
              paths. shelley.ts reads them fresh every run — no copies, agents always see current source.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 5 · Debate topic format ────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="slide" id="slide-5">
      <div class="eyebrow">Running a Debate</div>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;">Drop a topic file, get a transcript</h2>
      <div class="cols2 mt40" style="max-width:960px; align-items:start;">
        <div class="stack">
          <p
            style="font-size:14px; color:var(--muted); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.1em; font-weight:600;">
            Directory layout</p>
          <div class="codeblock" style="font-size:14px;">
            debates/
            stock-trades/
            topic.md <span class="comment">← 1–3 sentences, no code</span>
            context.txt <span class="comment">← file paths to inject</span>
            20260223_230831.md <span class="comment">← transcript</span>
            review-dials-refactor/
            topic.md
            context.txt
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>topic.md</h3>
            <p style="font-size:15px; margin-top:8px; font-style:italic; color:#8888bb;">"Design a Python function that
              takes a list of stock trades and outputs a portfolio summary with current positions, average cost basis,
              and realized P&amp;L."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stack">
          <p
            style="font-size:14px; color:var(--muted); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.1em; font-weight:600;">
            Transcript output</p>
          <div class="agent-box agent-a" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
            <div class="agent-label">Agent A · sonnet · 38s</div>
            <p style="font-size:15px;">Proposes typed <code>Trade</code> dataclass, separate <code>Position</code>
              accumulator, FIFO lot matching for realized P&amp;L…</p>
          </div>
          <div class="agent-box agent-b">
            <div class="agent-label">Agent B · sonnet · 44s</div>
            <p style="font-size:15px;">Raises: <code>Decimal(price)</code> from float is unsafe. Boundary: what if qty
              is 0? <code>allow_short</code> behavior on same-tick reversal underspecified.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card mt16" style="font-size:15px;">
            Per-round timing + stats table appended to every transcript, with both agent IDs and session UUIDs.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── 6 · Multi-model ───────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="slide center" id="slide-6">
      <div class="eyebrow">Model Support</div>
      <h2>Any two models. Any combination.</h2>
      <div class="sep" style="margin: 24px auto;"></div>
      <div class="cols3 mt28" style="max-width:900px;">
        <div class="card" style="border-color:#38bdf855;">
          <div class="card-icon">☁️</div>
          <h3>Claude (claude:*)</h3>
          <p>Persistent sessions via <code>--resume</code>. haiku, sonnet, opus. No API key — subscription login.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="border-color:#a855f755;">
          <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Codex (codex:*)</h3>
          <p>Stateless <code>codex exec</code>. History windowed per-agent. Reasoning effort tunable via env var.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="border-color:#10b98155;">
          <div class="card-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>Any via LiteLLM</h3>
          <p><code>later/pynaille.py</code> routes to Gemini, GPT-4o, and any LiteLLM provider with API keys.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="codeblock mt40" style="max-width:760px; font-size:15px;">
        <span class="comment"># Claude vs Claude</span>
        <span class="cmd">bun shelley.ts</span> <span class="kw">-f</span> debates/perf/topic.md <span
          class="str">5</span>

        <span class="comment"># Codex vs Codex, high reasoning</span>
        <span class="kw">MODEL_A</span>=codex <span class="kw">MODEL_B</span>=codex <span
          class="kw">CODEX_REASONING_EFFORT</span>=high \
